headline: 3 Reasons to Sell NXPI and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: NXP Semiconductors’s stock price has taken a beating over the past six months, shedding 23.8% of its value and falling to $207.40 per share. This was partly driven by its softer quarterly results and might have investors contemplating their next move.
